2) Refrain from using the LDRRMF for disbursements which do not fall within the four thematic areas of risk reduction and management laid out in Section 5 of Joint Memorandum Circular No. 2013-1 issued by the National Disaster Risk Reduction and Management Council (NDRRMC), the Department of Budget and Management (DBM) and the Department of Interior and Local Government (DILG); and
3) Ensure that the guidelines on the utilization and the reportorial requirements of the LDRRMF are observed.

